replies.content:
Well most people are stupid and tend to think inside the box. We have CC we have cash, it works okay for me. Why should I bother to ask myself could there be something better? Is there something wrong with the current system/s?
Sadly this comes with every new technology. The older people don't surprise me (my dad being an example, he has issues using an android TV that he got recently but has an android phone
), the younger ones do though. Let's see where 2015 takes us, as 2014 was a nice year but mostly monotonous.

